# ralph-orchestrator

This repository contains the **Ralph Orchestrator** CLI (`ralph`) plus its schemas, templates, and documentation.

## Quick start (local dev)

```bash
cd ralph-orchestrator
python -m pip install -e .
ralph --help
```

